285
00:23:09,680 --> 00:23:12,320
He wants the Linked Camp Horn?!

286
00:23:17,580 --> 00:23:19,720
Guo Youdao.

287
00:23:19,720 --> 00:23:23,340
You really do have more intentions than a hive of bees.

288
00:23:27,140 --> 00:23:28,780
Wine!

289
00:24:36,360 --> 00:24:38,060
That's right!

290
00:24:38,960 --> 00:24:40,980
It's this tune.

291
00:24:47,620 --> 00:24:48,820
What is this?

292
00:24:48,820 --> 00:24:52,580
Didn't you say that the wind in the stone room would urge the Linked Camp Horn

293
00:24:52,580 --> 00:24:55,240
to expand the force of the Pneuma of Sound?

294
00:24:55,240 --> 00:24:59,199
Master Chu Ming said you've lost your pneumatic powers so you can't fight it directly.

295
00:24:59,199 --> 00:25:01,940
You can only win by dodging.

296
00:25:01,940 --> 00:25:04,660
So I arranged the copper chimes in this formation.

297
00:25:04,660 --> 00:25:08,060
Later, I'll use the power of the sword to pick up the cobbles and hit the chimes.

298
00:25:08,060 --> 00:25:12,060
The cobbles rebound can simulate the track of the Pneuma of Sound.

299
00:25:12,060 --> 00:25:14,520
It can help you to practice.

300
00:25:17,340 --> 00:25:19,480
You are so clever.

301
00:25:20,020 --> 00:25:21,800
Did you come up with anything?

302
00:25:21,800 --> 00:25:24,100
Do you remember the day we were breaking the Pneumas?

303
00:25:24,100 --> 00:25:26,380
The song I hummed to you?

304
00:25:29,040 --> 00:25:32,200
I don't remember where I heard it,

305
00:25:32,200 --> 00:25:34,800
nor who sang it,

306
00:25:34,800 --> 00:25:36,820
but it's stuck in my mind.

307
00:25:37,280 --> 00:25:39,420
I know it's the song.

308
00:25:39,420 --> 00:25:41,639
This has something to do with the Linked Camped Horn?

309
00:25:41,639 --> 00:25:45,380
It does! When I was close to the Linked Camp Horn that day,

310
00:25:45,380 --> 00:25:50,740
the attacks that resonated with the wind were not irregular.

311
00:25:50,740 --> 00:25:54,120
It's the tune of that song.

312
00:25:54,760 --> 00:25:57,500
You mean that...

313
00:25:57,500 --> 00:26:01,400
As long as you know this song, you will know the direction of the next sound wave.

314
00:26:01,400 --> 00:26:06,000
As long as you can avoid the sound wave, you can walk up to the Linked Camp Horn.

315
00:26:06,580 --> 00:26:08,320
Are you ready then?

316
00:27:04,300 --> 00:27:05,860
Lu Ping.

317
00:27:06,880 --> 00:27:08,920
You are a worthy opponent.

318
00:27:08,920 --> 00:27:11,960
However, this is something I have to do.

319
00:27:13,040 --> 00:27:14,880
I am sorry.

320
00:27:31,140 --> 00:27:32,399
You're back too late.

321
00:27:32,400 --> 00:27:34,900
Tang Xiaomei said she has cleaned the kitchen.

322
00:27:34,900 --> 00:27:38,919
If you dare cook without her permission, she will break your leg tomorrow.

323
00:28:03,320 --> 00:28:07,960
Senior Huo Ying told me, this sweet cake is famous and difficult to buy.

324
00:28:07,960 --> 00:28:10,380
You usually have to line up for half a day to get it.

325
00:28:10,380 --> 00:28:12,560
How did you get it?

326
00:28:12,560 --> 00:28:16,560
Did you use your family's token or throw a big lady of the house tantrum?

327
00:28:16,560 --> 00:28:18,260
This isn't Kaifeng.

328
00:28:18,260 --> 00:28:20,580
The token is useless.

329
00:28:20,580 --> 00:28:23,560
I heard this shop is run by a husband and wife.

330
00:28:23,560 --> 00:28:26,160
I coaxed the boss, telling them that

331
00:28:26,840 --> 00:28:29,280
my husband is seriously ill,

332
00:28:29,280 --> 00:28:31,960
he has high fever and keeps saying nonsense.

333
00:28:31,960 --> 00:28:35,520
He really wants to eat your shop's sweet cake.

334
00:28:35,520 --> 00:28:39,400
The boss believed me and gave me the last box.

335
00:28:39,400 --> 00:28:43,680
Seeing how hard you've been practicing, consider it a reward.

336
00:28:45,040 --> 00:28:47,439
You've been so influenced by me that

337
00:28:47,440 --> 00:28:50,040
you don't even bat an eye when you lie now.

338
00:28:50,040 --> 00:28:55,360
Here! Sharing makes it more delicious.

339
00:28:59,720 --> 00:29:01,659
After spending so much time in Kaifeng.

340
00:29:01,659 --> 00:29:04,719
I love the laidback life here.

341
00:29:04,720 --> 00:29:06,460
Laidback?

342
00:29:06,460 --> 00:29:10,979
There are no fancy clothes or delicious food, plus you have to practice with me.

343
00:29:10,979 --> 00:29:12,660
You don't mind?

344
00:29:13,620 --> 00:29:16,160
I am the honor of the Qin Family.

345
00:29:17,160 --> 00:29:21,700
Of course, I had to help when I see how useless you've become.

346
00:29:21,700 --> 00:29:23,420
My honor.

347
00:29:23,420 --> 00:29:26,140
The martial arts of the Qin Family are secret.

348
00:29:26,140 --> 00:29:30,600
Now there's Miss Qin attentively teaching me.

349
00:29:31,120 --> 00:29:35,760
Such special treatment, am I already part of the family?

350
00:29:37,440 --> 00:29:40,679
Good for you, Lu Ping! You dare take advantage of me.

351
00:29:40,679 --> 00:29:42,420
Wait, didn't you say your husband is seriously ill?

352
00:29:42,420 --> 00:29:44,560
He has high fever and keeps saying nonsense?

353
00:29:46,900 --> 00:29:48,940
Wait! I am still eating.

354
00:30:09,740 --> 00:30:12,740
You… You two... single man and woman alone in a room?

355
00:30:12,740 --> 00:30:16,000
- What are you doing? You're feeding her?
- Young Lord Wei.

356
00:30:16,000 --> 00:30:18,860
Miss Qin is practicing a secret skill with me.

357
00:30:18,860 --> 00:30:21,920
Don't you always dread getting tired and having to work hard?

358
00:30:21,920 --> 00:30:24,060
Why are you here to make things harder for you?

359
00:30:24,060 --> 00:30:27,240
I was afraid you had some bad intentions towards Sangsang.

360
00:30:27,240 --> 00:30:28,959
Sangsang, it's time to leave.

361
00:30:28,959 --> 00:30:31,480
Do you plan on spending the night here?

362
00:30:33,460 --> 00:30:37,300
Qin Sang, let's practice tomorrow.

363
00:30:45,060 --> 00:30:46,540
See you tomorrow.

364
00:31:07,560 --> 00:31:08,899
Senior Huo Ying.

365
00:31:08,899 --> 00:31:13,940
You're not going cook Little White for dinner are you?

366
00:31:13,940 --> 00:31:17,919
Xiaomei, has it been our fault this whole time?

367
00:31:17,919 --> 00:31:20,600
We treat ourselves too much like losers.

368
00:31:21,140 --> 00:31:23,380
So others treat us as losers.

369
00:31:32,100 --> 00:31:34,420
I don't know when my courage

370
00:31:34,420 --> 00:31:37,260
had become even smaller than Little White's.

371
00:31:38,060 --> 00:31:41,440
Senior, I think Lu Ping can do it.

372
00:31:41,440 --> 00:31:46,179
Although he failed last time, I have a hunch that he will definitely succeed this time.

373
00:31:46,179 --> 00:31:49,299
Senior Huo, Eldest Senior went again.

374
00:31:50,040 --> 00:31:51,780
Again?

375
00:32:21,760 --> 00:32:23,639
Lu Ping, why are you still playing here?

376
00:32:23,640 --> 00:32:25,940
Eldest Senior has gone to the Seven Martyrs Court already.

377
00:32:32,400 --> 00:32:36,460
[Seven Martyrs Court]

378
00:32:58,940 --> 00:33:01,480
Guo Wushu, are you afraid of losing?

379
00:33:01,480 --> 00:33:04,080
How about you... drink some?

380
00:33:04,080 --> 00:33:05,859
Allay your fear!

381
00:33:18,640 --> 00:33:20,339
- He is coming. He is coming.
- What?

382
00:33:20,339 --> 00:33:23,419
However, it's not Lu Ping but Xu Weifeng.

383
00:33:27,260 --> 00:33:28,960
Is he afraid?

384
00:33:40,620 --> 00:33:42,679
Let's go, Guo Wushu.

385
00:33:42,680 --> 00:33:49,180
Let's see just exactly where your brother wanted to lead Lu Ping to.

386
00:34:12,770 --> 00:34:15,039
Xu Weifeng, you stole my steps.

387
00:34:15,039 --> 00:34:18,060
This is without morality. Is this a fair competition?

388
00:34:18,980 --> 00:34:21,939
There is only one Linked Camp Horn so how could there be a fair competition?

389
00:34:21,939 --> 00:34:25,080
On a battlefield , there is no morality, only winners or losers.

390
00:34:49,150 --> 00:34:50,900
Lu Ping.

391
00:34:50,900 --> 00:34:53,780
Neither one of us expected this last sound.

392
00:34:53,780 --> 00:34:55,410
You will die.

393
00:34:56,260 --> 00:35:00,020
I am already here, how can I just go back (empty handed)?

394
00:35:00,720 --> 00:35:03,060
The last thing I, Lu Ping, am afraid of is death.

395
00:35:03,720 --> 00:35:05,840
This is the place that my Master wanted me to come.

396
00:35:06,660 --> 00:35:10,980
I have to come, no matter the obstacles.

397
00:36:38,720 --> 00:36:41,020
To walk towards death.

398
00:36:42,220 --> 00:36:44,720
He really is crazy!

399
00:37:03,460 --> 00:37:06,119
Master, what's happening?

400
00:37:07,300 --> 00:37:09,220
Qin Sang.

401
00:37:09,860 --> 00:37:13,459
- Master Chu Min.
- Give him some time.

402
00:37:15,050 --> 00:37:18,880
[Seven Martyrs Court]

403
00:37:43,040 --> 00:37:47,200
This resonance, could it break the chain?

404
00:38:19,460 --> 00:38:25,170
[Seven Martyrs Court]

405
00:38:34,800 --> 00:38:38,200
Master, what happened?

406
00:38:46,110 --> 00:38:49,020
[Seven Martyrs Court]

407
00:38:56,300 --> 00:38:58,120
[Seven Martyrs Court]

408
00:39:23,380 --> 00:39:27,179
- This is the Linked Camp Horn?
- Let me see!

409
00:39:27,179 --> 00:39:31,539
I said he could do it! All of you owe me money, twenty five each.

410
00:39:33,580 --> 00:39:37,119
- Lu Ping, you are awesome.
- Yes, you are great.

411
00:39:48,400 --> 00:39:50,400
Impossible!

412
00:39:51,500 --> 00:39:54,360
How could I have lost?

413
00:39:55,620 --> 00:39:58,719
That kid has met a lot of impossibilities.

414
00:39:58,720 --> 00:40:03,660
Once, it was even "impossible" for him to live

415
00:40:03,660 --> 00:40:06,340
but he did.

416
00:40:40,660 --> 00:40:45,560
He broke the Seven Martyrs Court so casually.

417
00:40:45,560 --> 00:40:48,060
Do you look down on me?

418
00:40:48,640 --> 00:40:51,140
If you're that good, come back!

419
00:40:51,140 --> 00:40:52,819
Fight a good fight with me!

420
00:40:52,819 --> 00:40:54,820
Come on out!

421
00:40:54,820 --> 00:40:59,440
- Master, Guo Youdao has died already.
- Nonsense!

422
00:41:01,420 --> 00:41:04,100
He is just a coward.

423
00:41:04,100 --> 00:41:06,320
A turtle that is hiding in his shell!

424
00:41:07,320 --> 00:41:09,640
He promised me

425
00:41:11,120 --> 00:41:14,800
as long as I stayed in the Seven Martyrs Court,

426
00:41:14,800 --> 00:41:19,100
