440
00:42:07,700 --> 00:42:11,540
I can't live under his name my entire life!

441
00:42:11,540 --> 00:42:13,280
Elder,

442
00:42:16,220 --> 00:42:18,720
I know you still miss him.

443
00:42:21,940 --> 00:42:23,939
You don't want to believe he's died.

444
00:42:23,939 --> 00:42:26,720
I don't miss that old man.

445
00:42:29,880 --> 00:42:32,880
It was clearly him who didn't want to come back!

446
00:42:41,660 --> 00:42:43,740
Before Master died,

447
00:42:43,740 --> 00:42:46,360
