448
00:42:46,360 --> 00:42:48,760
I couldn't understand the meaning at that time.

449
00:42:49,680 --> 00:42:52,040
It's not until today that

450
00:42:52,880 --> 00:42:55,640
I understood what he meant.

451
00:42:58,380 --> 00:43:01,160
He told Master Chu Min to take me to the Big Dipper.

452
00:43:01,160 --> 00:43:03,780
He knew I would meet you.

453
00:43:03,780 --> 00:43:06,500
He used you to stimulate my competitive mind.

454
00:43:06,500 --> 00:43:09,000
He led me to the Seven Martyrs Court.

455
00:43:09,940 --> 00:43:13,900
He sealed my pneumatic powers temporarily by connecting his star to my destiny.

